          "text": "Confirmed -- the CTO agrees to have the candidate explain the discrepancies before an offer decision. This is a pragmatic resolution.\n\n**Agreed path forward:**\n1. Chen Jing will arrange a call with Wang Hao to discuss the background check findings\n2. Findings will be presented factually (not accusatorily)\n3. Offer decision and level will depend on the candidate's response\n4. CTO expects results as soon as possible\n\nThis approach preserves the hiring opportunity (CTO's priority) while maintaining background check integrity (HR's responsibility). The candidate's response to the direct conversation will be the decisive input.\n\nI'll document the agreed path in the candidate file."
